# Core hybrid-style (photo + comic)

**Prompt (copy‚Äìpaste):**
*‚ÄúAlbum cover art for ‚ÄòTo The Band‚Äô by Steve Chill. A band celebrating after rehearsal, tipsy, laughing together. The lead figure‚Äîa man with dreadlocks in a green shirt‚Äîstands slightly forward as the clear main character, confident grin, charismatic eyes. The rest of the band is behind him, looser and a bit blurred, cheering and playing around. Nighttime outdoor vibe like stepping out of a rehearsal space: cold air, street-lamp glow, slight breath vapor, scattered beer bottles, spontaneous joy. Photo‚Äìcomic hybrid: natural flash photography + subtle ink outlines, soft halftone shading, gentle motion blur, high micro-detail skin, cinematic depth of field. Moody yet warm palette (amber lights, cool shadows, green accents). Leave clean space for title at top.‚Äù*

